            "reviews": "“...creates an intimate and tangible experience out of recent history.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/01/17/bury-me-my-love-creates-an-intimate-tangible-experience-out-recent-history/?utm_term=.4975c0c8b44a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Washington Post</a><br><br>“...Bury Me, My Love is one of the best story-based games we’ve ever played.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://metro.co.uk/2019/01/09/bury-me-my-love-switch-review-text-misadventure-8324278/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Metro</a><br><br>“...an eye-opening tale that's equal parts heartbreaking, terrifying, and inspiring.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/bury-me-my-love-review-trials-and-tribulations/1900-6417060/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamespot</a><br>",
